<div class="drizzle-o-ContentGrouping">
  <p class="drizzle-b-P">In order to implement Spark-Core, you'll need to create a
        kit on <a class="drizzle-b-Link" href="https://typekit.com">Typekit.com</a> for your application.</p>

  <p class="drizzle-b-P">Need access to typekit for your internal Quicken Loans application? Email
    <a class="drizzle-b-Link" href="mailto:sparkdesignsystem@quickenloans.com">sparkdesignsystem@quickenloans.com</a>
  </p>

  <p class="drizzle-b-P">The kit should include two font families, but you should only add the listed weights. We
    currently do not use italics in our type treatment.</p>

  <ul class="drizzle-b-List">
    <li class="drizzle-b-List__item">
      <a class="drizzle-b-Link drizzle-b-Label" href="https://typekit.com/fonts/myriad">Myriad Pro</a>
      <ul class="drizzle-b-List drizzle-b-List--nested">
        <li class="drizzle-b-List__item">Regular (400)</li>
        <li class="drizzle-b-List__item">Bold (700)</li>
      </ul>
    </li>
    <li class="drizzle-b-List__item">
      <a class="drizzle-b-Link drizzle-b-Label" href="https://typekit.com/fonts/quatro-slab">Quatro Slab</a>
      <ul class="drizzle-b-List drizzle-b-List--nested">
        <li class="drizzle-b-List__item">Regular (400)</li>
        <li class="drizzle-b-List__item">Bold (700)</li>
      </ul>
    </li>
  </ul>

  <p class="drizzle-b-P">Please see
    <a class="drizzle-b-Link" href="/patterns/elements/typography.html">Typography</a> for font usage.
  </p>
